reviews.text: The worst service , ask the guy at the counter whats the difference with the few sets they have the sales guy was very rude and instead of helping me out understand what is what he told me off course that one more ??? Im like hello ? Im asking u can reply me in a polite way but no ? Why because im a indian not local HK residence is it ? Ure chinese im indian ?? This is being clearly raciss !!! Haagen dazs ? What action is going to be taken ?? I have a vdo recording showing the guy who was rude showing his back to me and i also made a complaint to customer service of the management near your shop ... i will be waiting for a reply on what action is being taken againts this racist staff of yours !!!!
Staff not as professional as before.  If you are doing a two or three scopes, they used to remind you which favor to eat first according to the taste, etc.
They were so many staff , but not many customers. They are large range of Ice -cream to choose from .
On 9th June I was charged 148 HK dollars for 3 small tubs of ice cream.  What is the real cost of 2 vanilla and 1 lemon sorbet singe scoop?  I think I was charged too much.
Not enough seats.  Not as good as the old location in TST.  I think this is the only location in Kowloon that provides table service.
